data.description: Step into a fusion of modernity and comfort with this renovated bungalow, nestled in the heart of 16 Tech. Just a stone's throw away from the vibrant Guggman Haus Brewery, The AMP, and the iconic Taggart Memorial, where summer evenings come alive with concerts and plays. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, looking to downsize, or an investor eyeing a prime Airbnb spot, this home is a tech-lover's dream and a haven of convenience. The custom Philips Hue indoor and outdoor lighting sets the mood. BONUS: All furniture/lighting/mirrors/chairs/art/tables/Buddy figures are included with the sale of property.
